name: Bound Shibari From Behind
description:
Coffee for me senpai? 👉👈🥹

https://ko-fi.com/barjoe01

!!! EXPERIMENTAL !!!

A LoRA to bound a damsel's arms behind back with from behind angle, Currently fully experimental due to the nature of fingers and hands on AI image generation

Strength : 1 - 0.8

Trigger word :

bound, arms behind back, from behind

Known problem/more info :

  • You can try to experimenting with adding negative embedding or better hand Locon to lower the chance of messing up fingers and hands negative_hand Negative Embedding (https://civitai.com/models/56519/negativehand-negative-embedding), EnvyBetterHands LoCon (https://civitai.com/models/47085/envybetterhands-locon)

  • Just like gacha, when you got a good result, you got a good result

  • Most of the time, you might need to inpaint some of the hands and fingers to get a much better result

  • hires fix could also help to make the fingers more detailed

  • If you have more suggestion to even make this better, you can contact me at AI Waifu DID Discord Server : https://discord.gg/9P5rEKwQ4N

  • Not tested in realistic model
